<item>
            <title>[LU-15766] Improve manual page lfs-hsm.1 to match options and text in lfs.c</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15766</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Current manual page lfs-hsm.1 has minor inconsistent formatting issues such as:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
lfs hsm_state &amp;lt;FILE&amp;gt;...
lfs hsm_action file
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;and missing argument in option&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
[--archive-id]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;According to lfs.c the options are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
{&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;hsm_set&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, lfs_hsm_set, 0, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Set HSM user flag on specified files.\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
	 &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;usage: hsm_set [--norelease] [--noarchive] [--dirty] [--exists] &quot;&lt;/span&gt;
	 &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;[--archived] [--lost] [--archive-id NUM] &amp;lt;file&amp;gt; ...&quot;&lt;/span&gt;}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The provided patch ensure that the manual page and options in lfs.c are in match and consistent.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Debian GNU/Linux 11 (bullseye)</environment>
